product_description: Dull, thinning hair stopping you from trying out your favourite hairstyles? The L’Oreal Fall Repair Anti-hair fall Shampoo 3X is the answer for all your hair care worries. It has a unique blend of hair-loving ingredients to give you thicker, smoother and shinier hair you’ll love to flaunt. This shampoo offers a triple-action anti hair fall treatment that nourishes the hair roots and follicles, strengthens and reconstructs hair shaft, and promotes thicker hair growth. It is formulated with arginine to help nourish the hair from root to tip. Arginine is a natural amino acid, one that is produced by the human body. It works to enhance the blood supply to the scalp and hair follicles for complete nourishment. This way, arginine stimulates and encourages faster hair growth and helps each strand regain its natural thickness. Say goodbye to all your hair care problems and get saloon-like results instantly with this L’Oreal shampoo. Just apply ample amount of shampoo on wet hair, massage gently with your fingertips and rinse off. This anti hair fall shampoo from L’Oreal is also effective in cleansing hair of oil and dirt, leaving it soft, clean and shiny.

This unique combination of Keratin and Argan Oil conditions and strengthens your hair and provides them hydration and elasticity. With its dual action, TRESemmé Keratin Smooth Shampoo helps you get up to 100% smoother hair with more shine. Recommended by professionals, the TRESemmé Keratin Smooth Shampoo is especially formulated for Indian hair and is suitable for both naturally and chemically treated hair. It is also suitable for use in conjunction with any oil treatments. Now, get visibly straighter, smoother hair that is easier to style hair. product_description: This refreshing formula blends the natural sap of the margosa and euphorbia trees with the bhringraj herb to control dandruff. Eliminates the dryness, flaking and itching associated with dandruff. Special pH balanced formula is gentle enough for use every day. Leaves hair fresh, lustrous and full of natural body.   Dandruff and an itchy scalp can prove to be quite an embarrassing problem for many. While dandruff solutions are aplenty, the complex combination of chemicals usually causes more damage than repair, leaving behind rough and lifeless hair. Biotique’s Bio Margosa Fresh Daily Dandruff Expertise shampoo and conditioner brings together the goodness of ayurveda to give hair that is lustrous, silky, and dandruff-free.This special formulation combines the natural sap of the margosa tree along with bhringraj and euphorbia to gently cleanse your scalp and leave hair feeling soft, luxurious, and manageable. Bhringraj helps arrest hair fall and promote hair growth, while neem reduces hair thinning, adding the adequate amount of moisture.The Bio Margosa Fresh Daily Dandruff Expertise shampoo contains a gentle pH formula that is safe enough for everyday use. Regular use reduces dryness, flakiness, and itching of the scalp considerably. Also, it combines the benefits of a conditioner along with the shampoo, reducing the need for additional products. It is suitable for all hair types.Take an adequate amount of shampoo and conditioner on your palm and massage gently onto wet hair. Work up a rich lather and then rinse off.

product_description: Biotique Botanicals introduces an awesome blend of henna leaves, beryberry and soap nut extracts, all in one shampoo. These essential herbal properties present in the shampoo cleanse your scalp, providing deep nourishment to your hair and its intense conditioning formula adds volume to your hair. Your hair will become irresistibly soft. The Biotique shampoo smoothes the texture of your hair and the goodness of henna conditions your hair by adding shine and volume to it. The shampoo is enriched with real botanical extracts. For rich dark tones use the Biotique Bio Henna Leaf Fresh Texture Shampoo and Conditioner and flaunt your beautiful hair. Biotique herbals products are all made from organic herbs. The products they manufacture are all bio-degradable and environment friendly. They provide Ayurvedic solutions for skin, hair, and body problems. The shampoo densifies your hair making it thick, shiny and lustrous. The product is combination of Mehndi (Lawsonia alba), Mulethi (Glycyrrhiza glabra), Brahmi (Hydrocotyle asiatica), Aam beej (Magnifera indica), and other valuable herbs that cleanse and condition your hair. Apply the shampoo on wet hair, lather through the strands and rinse thoroughly with water. You can repeat the process if needed. The Biotique shampoo comes in a 210 ml bottle. Daily use of the product also prevents premature greying of hair. The shampoo is infused with pure herbal extracts that have no harmful effects. The product is free from preservatives and synthetic fragrances. This product is definitely worth a try. Buy the Biotique Shampoo and Conditioner 210ml and get gorgeous and lustrous hair..

product_description: This refreshing formula is blended with pure green apple extract, sea algae and centella, to purify and nourish the scalp and hair with natural minerals and proteins. Special pH balanced formula is gentle enough to use every day. Leaves hair refreshed and full of natural body and shine.   Opting for the right shampoo to your hair and scalp is very important for the maintenance of a healthy hair. Biotique Green Apple Purifying Shampoo and Conditioner comes with a blend of green apple extract, centella, and sea algae to provide your hair with vital minerals and proteins, making it healthy and shiny. This shampoo is apt for daily usage and doesn’t dry your scalp, retaining the natural shine and body of the hair.Biotique Daily Purifying Shampoo and Conditioner is ideal for oily hair and scalp. The formula of the shampoo has a balanced pH, which makes it treat your hair gently, providing sufficient nourishment. Green apple extracts cleanses your scalp and makes it oil free, thereby refreshing your hair.This product is a mixture of shampoo and conditioner, and thus you needn’t buy an extra conditioner for your hair. The shampoo helps in bringing volume to your hair whereas the conditioner helps in bringing shine. It helps you in getting rid of your dandruff and itchy scalp. The ingredients of the product are Chinai Ghas, Manduk parni, Shikakai, Seb, Badam tail, Nariyal tail, Himalayan water, and Ayurvedic medicine. This shampoo is completely organic and free of preservatives.Apply this product generously on your wet hair, work lather, and gently massage your hair till scalp. Do not let your eye come in contact with the shampoo.

Benefit Specially formulated for men with a unique male fragrance. Benefit Its formula. with citrus extracts, freshens lifeless hair. while leaving hair up to 100% flake free. Benefit Leaves your hair dandruff free and gives a beautiful black shine. Benefit Softens and smoothes frizzy hair while making It dandruff free. Anti fungal ingredients reduce the amount of fungus on the scalp, therefore fighting the leading cause of dandruff. These ingredients include Zinc Pyrithione (ZPT) and selenium sulfide. Anti-proliferative agents slow down the production of skin cells without necessarily acting directly against the fungus. One such ingredient is coal tar, which primarily fights signs of dandruff. Keratolytic agents break down the intercellular bond (keratin) that holds skin cells together on the uppermost layer of the scalp. Therefore, when the top layer of cells are shed, they are separate rather than in clumps. These agents include sulfur and salicylic acid, which, again, primarily fights signs and not the cause of dandruff.

product_description: Rescue hair from damage, dullness, and hairfall. Helps repair damaged hair to create smoothness, and reduces breakage for up to 10X stronger hair (strength against damage vs. non-conditioning shampoo). Gentle enough for everyday use, even for color or chemically treated hair. Formulated with Head and Shoulders’ Fresh Scent Technology featuring enhanced fragrance notes for an improved in-shower scent experience up to 100% dandruff free. Visible flakes with regular use.   Benefit Specially designed to improve the condition of the scalp and help rescue hair from the damage caused by modern lifestyles. Benefit An intensely invigorating clean and dandruff free hair. Benefit Contains natural menthol for a cooling sensation. Benefit Moisturises dry scalps and makes them dandruff free. Benefit Specially formulated for men with a unique male fragrance. Benefit Its formula. with citrus extracts, freshens lifeless hair. while leaving hair up to 100% flake free. Benefit Leaves your hair dandruff free and gives a beautiful black shine. Benefit Softens and smoothes frizzy hair while making It dandruff free. Anti fungal ingredients reduce the amount of fungus on the scalp, therefore fighting the leading cause of dandruff. These ingredients include Zinc Pyrithione (ZPT) and selenium sulfide. Anti-proliferative agents slow down the production of skin cells without necessarily acting directly against the fungus. One such ingredient is coal tar, which primarily fights signs of dandruff. Keratolytic agents break down the intercellular bond (keratin) that holds skin cells together on the uppermost layer of the scalp. Therefore, when the top layer of cells are shed, they are separate rather than in clumps. These agents include sulfur and salicylic acid, which, again, primarily fights signs and not the cause of dandruff.
